 Director is operating with limitless emergency purchasing authority. Physical and human resources have been distributed as follows:\n*   **Medical/Safety:** Concentrated at the main entrances to form a secure triage perimeter with external EMS.\n*   **Environmental:** On-site teams deployed to perimeter storm drains (defensive only). External heavy resources routed to the main outflow points leading to international waterways.\n*   **Engineering/Trades:** Temporarily distributed to utility hubs to cut off power and gas, then immediately evacuated to muster zones.\n*   **Management/HR:** Centralized in the ICC (Admin Building) and at muster points for personnel accountability and external communication.\n\nThis operational framework ensures the absolute prioritization of human life, swift environmental mitigation, and seamless integration with incoming federal and local emergency responders.",
